{"tid":1508334,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南韓政府：向香港發出旅遊警示","createTime":"2019-08-26T13:23:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T13:40:46.000Z","uid":20933,"like":61,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d0ff5f5ff944d1ea1a067727fcc400c8d1e0ff92","tid":1508334,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:23:37.000Z","msg":"南韓向香港發出旅遊警示，級別屬第一級的藍色警報，南韓外交部表示，香港遊行示威持續，抗議者與警察衝突不斷升級，提醒準備到港旅遊及在香港的僑民在事態穩定之前注意安全，今後將視情況，上調或解除對香港的旅遊警報。<br />\n<br />\n南韓的旅遊警示級別分4級，由低至高依次是藍色 (注意風險)、黃色(謹慎前往)、紅色(撤離)，及黑色(禁止旅行)。特區政府早前表示，由於修例示威接連引發激烈衝突，有22個國家及地區對香港發出旅遊警示。"},{"pid":"a67c29e2176fb99c74d9ddcc1d488371eace3c15","tid":1508334,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:23:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1157610&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1157610%26csid%3D261_341&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsTMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=0ca9c1d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1157610&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"f9232bbe21ab0abb8515d40d4f7061b9ec102496","tid":1508334,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:24:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最新post 睇得清楚d + 加左明天有義士再審係頂！</span></span>(極正經)(請推至長期置頂)被捕義士進程，一個也不能少不只是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1508237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1508237</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3138a32e7b0923ddba867f3e7ae4b3a05e1d9710","tid":1508334,"uid":200083,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:24:26.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 還我韓妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"098ff68533f97ace0071d009125a7f3f74b63f8a","tid":1508334,"uid":23416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:25:47